text: Ellen Mabel Liederskron Babington was an archer from Great Britain. She was born on 12 June 1877 and died on 10 September 1956. Babington competed at the 1908 Summer Olympics.Nellie Babington == References == Category:1877 births Category:1956 deaths Category:British archers Category:Olympians for Great Britain
